---
// Revenue Streams section component
---

<section class='py-16 md:py-0 relative overflow-hidden px-4'>
  <div class='max-w-[90rem] mx-auto bg-[#024349] rounded-2xl pt-8 md:pt-[5.5rem] md:pb-[4.68rem]'>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class='text-center flex flex-col gap-6 mb-10'>
      <span class='badge-secondary'> HOW IT WORKS </span>
      <h2
        class='text-white font-semibold text-2xl md:text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em]'
      >
        One SDK, Multiple Revenue <br />
        Streams
      </h2>

      <p
        class='text-white text-base leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal max-w-[32rem] mx-auto'
      >
        NetSignal SDK collects real-world signal data from your app (with user consent), helping
        mobile operators improve coverage and performance â€” and pays you monthly based on active
        users and geolocation demand.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p
      class='gradient-text text-base md:text-lg text-center leading-6 font-medium max-w-md tracking-[-0.02em] mx-auto'
    >
      No user data is ever sold or linked to identity. Integration is light, privacy-compliant, and
      fully transparent.
    </p>

    <!-- Central Illustration with Flow -->
    <div class='relative mb-[6.875rem] mt-[5.75rem]'>
      <!-- Central Image -->
      <div class='flex justify-center lg:max-w-[1253px] mx-auto mb-16'>
        <img
          src='/assets/decoratives/HowItWorks.png'
          alt='How NetSignal SDK works - Revenue flow illustration'
          class='w-auto h-auto object-cover'
          loading='lazy'
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What you get in return -->
    <div class='text-center'>
      <h4
        class='text-white font-semibold text-lg tracking-[-0.02em] py-[0.625rem] px-[1.25rem] rounded-full bg-[#012E3280] w-fit mx-auto mb-12'
      >
        What you get in return:
      </h4>

      <div class='flex gap-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-center'>
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div
          class='flex gap-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg py-4 px-6 md:p-8 text-left items-center'
        >
          <img src='/assets/icons/plug.png' alt='Code' class='w-10 h-10' />

          <h4 class='text-white font-semibold text-sm'>
            Quick and easy integration with just a few lines of code. Our SDK is light,
            privacy-friendly, and works in the background without affecting your app's performance.
          </h4>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div
          class='flex gap-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg py-4 px-6 md:p-8 text-left items-center'
        >
          <img src='/assets/icons/chart.png' alt='Code' class='w-10 h-10' />
          <h4 class='text-white font-semibold text-sm'>
            Earn monthly revenue from real-world network data while helping improve mobile coverage
            and connectivity for users around the world.
          </h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(91.29deg, #beffd7 6.51%, #8ed5db 86.05%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
</style>
